# Mobile/web bundle — generated by `npm run build:mobile` (Vite wipes and
# rewrites the whole dir, content-hashed asset names). Committing it into
# feature branches makes every two in-flight PRs conflict on the hashed
# filenames + index.html <script src>. Instead it is built + committed to
# `main` ONLY by .github/workflows/build-mobile-bundle.yml on push to main.
# True source lives in src/renderer/ + src/renderer/public/. Do NOT hand-edit
# anything under mobile/www/ — it will be overwritten by the next build.
mobile/www/
